Name: LATITUDE CENTISECOND (ANGULAR)
Explanation: ONE OF 100 EQUAL PARTS OF A SECOND, THE TOTAL OF 100 SUCH PARTS IS EQUAL TO ONE SECOND OF LATITUDE.

Name: LONGITUDE CENTISECOND (ANGULAR)
Explanation: ONE OF 100 EQUAL PARTS OF A SECOND, THE TOTAL OF 100 SUCH PARTS IS EQUAL TO ONE SECOND OF LONGITUDE.
